 Demand)</summary>\n\n<table>\n<tr><th>Name</th><th align=\"right\">Enrollment</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th><th align=\"right\">% of 大学 Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td>北海道大学</td><td align=\"right\">17,770</td><td align=\"right\">1,185</td><td align=\"right\">49.60%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>はこだて未来大学</td><td align=\"right\">1,207</td><td align=\"right\">966</td><td align=\"right\">40.44%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>函館大学</td><td align=\"right\">297</td><td align=\"right\">238</td><td align=\"right\">9.96%</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n<details>\n<summary>特別支援学校 (Special Needs Schools) — 592 Students (0.30% of Total Demand)</summary>\n\n<table>\n<tr><th>Name</th><th align=\"right\">Modeled Demand</th><th align=\"right\">% of 特別支援学校 Demand</th></tr>\n<tr><td>七飯養護学校</td><td align=\"right\">234</td><td align=\"right\">39.53%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>七飯養護学校おしま学園分校</td><td align=\"right\">79</td><td align=\"right\">13.34%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>北海道教育大学附属特別支援学校</td><td align=\"right\">73</td><td align=\"right\">12.33%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>函館五稜郭養護学校</td><td align=\"right\">65</td><td align=\"right\">10.98%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>函館盲学校</td><td align=\"right\">58</td><td align=\"right\">9.80%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>函館聾学校</td><td align=\"right\">58</td><td align=\"right\">9.80%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>函館養護学校</td><td align=\"right\">24</td><td align=\"right\">4.05%</td></tr>\n<tr><td>ゆうあい養護学校高等部</td><td align=\"right\">1</td><td align=\"right\">0.17%</td></tr>\n</table>\n\n</details>\n\n## Methodology\n\nResident and commuter totals are derived from employed persons (就業者数) and workers (従業者数) per small census area (小地域), refined by 500m labor mesh and 250m/100m resident mesh to achieve sub-district point placement. Population counts are conserved at the 小地域 level, and point placement is optimized via a mesh-aware loss function.\n\nCommute patterns are modeled using a gravity model augmented by known origin-destination flows at the municipality (市町村) or designated city ward (区) level.\n\n## Data Sources\n\n- 令和2年国勢調査 (2020 National Census) — [e-Stat](https://www.e-stat.go.jp/)\n- 令和3年経済センサス (2021 Economic Census) — [e-Stat](https://www.e-stat.go.jp/)\n- 簡易100mメッシュ人口 (100m Mesh Population) — [GTFS-GIS](https://gtfs-gis.jp/teikyo/)\n- 国土数値情報 (National Land Numerical Information) — [MLIT](https://nlftp.mlit.go.jp/)\n- 空港管理状況調査 (Airport Management Statistics) — [MLIT Aviation](https://www.mlit.go.jp/koku/15_bf_000185.html)\n- 港湾調査 (Port Survey) — [MLIT Ports](https://www.mlit.go.jp/k-toukei/kouwan.html)\n- 大学ポートレート (University Portraits) — [JASSO](https://portraits.niad.ac.jp/)\n- 学校基本調査 (School Basic Survey) — [MEXT](https://www.mext.go.jp/)\n- 観光統計 (Tourism Statistics) — [JNTO](https://statistics.jnto.go.jp/)\n- Overture Maps Foundation — [Overture](https://overturemaps.org/)\n- 海しる / J-EGG500 (Ocean Information / Bathymetry) — [MSIL](https://www.msil.go.jp/) / [JODC](https://www.jodc.go.jp/)\n\n## License\n\nThis map data is released under the [MIT License](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT).\n\n## Attribution\n\nData derived from the following government and public data sources. See **Data Sources** above for links.\n\n- **Population & Commuting**: 令和2年国勢調査 (2020 National Census), 令和3年経済センサス (2021 Economic Census)\n- **Geospatial**: 国土数値情報 (National Land Numerical Information), Overture Maps Foundation\n- **Institutions**: 学校基本調査, 大学ポートレート, 空港管理状況調査, 港湾調査\n- **Tourism**: 観光統計 (Tourism Statistics)\n- **Bathymetry**: 海しる / J-EGG500",
